        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Federal Adjustment of Income Rates Act or the FAIR Act</b></p> <p>This bill modifies pay rates for federal employees in 2022. Specifically, the bill increases rates under the statutory pay systems and for prevailing rate employees by 4.1% and increases locality pay by 1%.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
